Subject: You...You Don't Like My Webcomic?
Description: Sadly it happens to us all at one time or another...and people aren't always so kind about it! Join Laura Cascos and Erika Wagner (the team behind the amazing Webcomic Sidekick Girl), BluRaven C. Houvener (writer and illustrator of It's Just another day), and Jon David (creative force behind the novel series Morgalla) as they walk you through the ins and outs of how to cope with criticism and survive to create another day!    Speakers include:BluRaven C. Houvener, Laura Cascos, Erika Wagner  - Track: Webcomics  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
